OL,3,CBorders Book Festival programme
OL,4,Claunches
OL,6,FThe Borders Book Festival's programme
OL,7,Fhas been announced, as Melrose gears
OL,8,Fup for four days of bookish adventures
OL,9,Fat Melrose's Harmony Garden from
OL,10,FThursday June 11th to 14th.
OL,12,FThe Festival promises political debate
OL,13,Fand new fiction treats as well as
OL,14,Fcomedians and sports stars with tales
OL,15,Fof willpower, skill and endurance.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
