OL,3,CBorders Book Festival programme
OL,4,Claunches
OL,6,FFestival Directors, Alistair Moffat
OL,7,Fand Paula Ogilvie, said: "Never more
OL,8,Fthan now have we needed a reason to
OL,9,Fgather, to celebrate our shared
OL,10,Ffriendships, to debate, to ponder, and
OL,11,Fto try to see a way through the chaos
OL,12,Fof our world."
OL,14,FThe political line-up includes:
OL,16,FOther well-known faces from the small
OL,17,Fscreen this year include:
OL,19,FLegends from the worlds of culture and
OL,20,Fsport include:
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
