OL,3,CBorders Book Festival programme
OL,4,Claunches
OL,6,FThe line-up of storytellers features:
OL,8,FThe Festival Directors say that it
OL,9,Fwill be a space to escape our daily
OL,10,Flives, "but it also, vitally, offers
OL,11,Fmyriad opportunities to hear some of
OL,12,Fthe best minds on the planet ponder
OL,13,Fthe crises of our modern world and
OL,14,Fdiscuss the ways in which we, as
OL,15,Findividuals can make a difference and
OL,16,Fuse our own personal agency for good."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
