OL,3,CBorders Book Festival programme
OL,4,Claunches
OL,6,FThere will also be a Family Book
OL,7,FFestival and the Walter Scott Prize
OL,8,Ffor Historical Fiction will be awarded
OL,9,Fduring the opening evening of the
OL,10,FFestival. The shortlisted authors for
OL,11,Fthat are:
OL,13,FAs well as all of the literature, the
OL,14,Fevent will include live music in the
OL,15,FOrchard Food Village.
OL,17,FRebecca Edser, Head of EventScotland,
OL,18,Fsays she hopes it will "make a
OL,19,Fpositive contribution to the local
OL,20,Fcommunity and the wider visitor
OL,21,Feconomy."
